Axis-Shield Reaffirms Recommendation to Reject Offer From Alere

-- B y   P e t e r   W o o d i f i e l d
-- 
2011-09-19T06:06:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-19/axis-shield-reaffirms-recommendation-to-reject-offer-from-alere.html
Axis-Shield Plc (ASD)  reaffirmed its
recommendation that investors should reject the 460 pence a
share offer from Alere AS Holdings Ltd. as it undervalues the
company and its prospects.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter Woodifield at 
 pwoodifield@bloomberg.net  